settings.description: Venture through a switch-and-money-filled world of speedrunning, careful timing, precise jumps, and more! There's also an E-Coin up high in space, waiting to be found!
My First Level! So This is a fun level to play. There's also a secret ending by going to the chest. To do this, you have to step on the note blocks, Step on P-switch, and run to the chest.
Muchas gracias por jugar el nivel tutorial de youtube. No soy una multicuenta de otra persona
Mario Finds his castle and must go through it in order to win, the big bad bowser is waiting for him, but is it really the end? Bowser's Airship 1 is next.
A fortress filled with interesting contraptions Bowser threw in.
A long and vegetable filled adventure. A mini Mario game I guess?
Luigi has teamed up with bowser to take over the mushroom kingdom using the advanced P-wing, Mario must take the advanced P-wing from the chest to halfway stop the invasion.
